              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM186867">Section 304(3)</extref> of the principal Act</citation> is amended by omitting the word <amend.in quote="1">disability</amend.in>, and substituting the words <amend.in quote="1">inability to adequately perform the duties of office</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
